Package net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.dnd

Drag and drop API.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DragSource
    The source of a drag and drop operation.
    DropLocationIdentifier
    Identifies a portion in the drop target area.
    DropOption
    Defines an option when dropping on a target.
    DropTarget
    The target of a drag and drop operation.
    Transferable
    Interface defining data that can be transfered between two objects.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DnDUtil
    Utility class for drag and drop operations.
    DropLocation
    Describes the location of a drop in relationship to the drop target.
    FieldComponentDropTarget
    A drop target to copy String data into a Field.
    ListElementTransferable
    List transferable.
    ResourceDragSource
    A drag source for a single resource.
    ResourceTransferable
    A transferable for a Resource.
    SimpleDragSource
    A simple implementation of DragSource that returns an object with a single content type.
    SimpleDropOption
    A drop option with properties for all fields.
    SimpleEntityTransferable
    Ensures the entity returned by SimpleTransferable.getTransferData(ContentType) is attached.
    SimpleTransferable
    Returns an object of any type with a single content type.
    StringTransferable
    A transferable representing a String.
    VerticalContainerDropTarget
    A drop target to be used on components within a container.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AboveBelow
    An enum for dropping above or below the target.
    AboveBelowUpon
    An enum for dropping above, upon or below the target.
    TreeNodeAboveBelowChild
    Drop locations for tree nodes.
